Prompt:

"Create a stunning fusion of AI and Indian culture. Imagine a futuristic scene where advanced AI technology blends harmoniously with traditional Indian elements. Show a majestic robotic figure adorned with intricate patterns inspired by henna art, wearing futuristic versions of Indian attire like a saree or kurta. Surround it with floating holograms resembling mandalas and Sanskrit scripts. Include a vibrant background representing iconic Indian elements—temples, peacocks, and lotus flowers—merging with futuristic cityscapes and neon-lit AI circuits. Use warm colors like gold, maroon, and saffron to represent tradition, alongside cool blues and purples to reflect technology."

This prompt should produce a visually rich, balanced mix of AI aesthetics and India’s cultural essence.

